@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ywwgfr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v0 + 0.74)) + 0.37)
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.73) + wp.abs(v0 + 0.13)) + ((tmp + 0.52 + tmp + 0.65) * (v2 + 0.78 * tmp + 0.47)))
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
